---
export const prerender = true;
---

<html lang="de">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <meta name="robots" content="noindex, nofollow" />
  <title>Spektrum — Malerbetrieb & Farbgestaltung in Trier</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Spektrum — Malerbetrieb und Farbgestaltung in Trier. Fassaden, Innenraeume, kreative Techniken. Seit 2011." />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Outfit:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />

  <style>
    html { overflow-x: hidden; }
    /* ===== RESET & BASE ===== */
    *, *::before, *::after {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    html {
      scroll-behavior: smooth;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
      color: #1E1E2E;
      background-color: #FAFAFA;
      line-height: 1.7;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    img {
      max-width: 100%;
      height: auto;
      display: block;
    }

    a {
      text-decoration: none;
      color: inherit;
    }

    h1, h2, h3, h4 {
      font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.15;
    }

    /* ===== NAVBAR ===== */
    .navbar {
      position: fixed;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      z-index: 100;
      background: rgba(250, 250, 250, 0.85);
      backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
      -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
      padding: 1rem 2rem;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.12);
    }

    .navbar-brand {
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6366F1, #F472B6);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
    }

    .navbar-links {
      display: flex;
      gap: 2rem;
      list-style: none;
    }

    .navbar-links a {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #1E1E2E;
      transition: color 0.3s ease;
      position: relative;
    }

    .navbar-links a::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      bottom: -4px;
      left: 0;
      width: 0;
      height: 2px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #6366F1, #F472B6);
      border-radius: 2px;
      transition: width 0.3s ease;
    }

    .navbar-links a:hover::after {
      width: 100%;
    }

    .navbar-cta {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      padding: 0.55rem 1.4rem;
      border-radius: 50px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6366F1, #8B5CF6);
      color: #fff;
      transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
    }

    .navbar-cta:hover {
      transform: translateY(-1px);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.3);
    }

    /* Mobile menu */
    .menu-toggle {
      display: none;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 5px;
      background: none;
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      padding: 4px;
    }

    .menu-toggle span {
      display: block;
      width: 24px;
      height: 2px;
      background: #1E1E2E;
      border-radius: 2px;
      transition: transform 0.3s ease, opacity 0.3s ease;
    }

    /* ===== HERO ===== */
    .hero {
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 7rem 2rem 4rem;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .hero-inner {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      width: 100%;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.2fr;
      gap: 3rem;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .hero-text {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
    }

    .hero-text h1 {
      font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 5.5vw, 4.5rem);
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
      color: #1E1E2E;
      margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    }

    .hero-text h1 span {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6366F1, #F472B6, #2DD4BF);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
    }

    .hero-subtitle {
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      font-weight: 400;
      color: #64748B;
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .hero-subtitle strong {
      color: #1E1E2E;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .hero-cta {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      padding: 0.9rem 2rem;
      border-radius: 50px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6366F1, #8B5CF6);
      color: #fff;
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
    }

    .hero-cta:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 12px 32px rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.35);
    }

    .hero-cta span {
      -webkit-text-fill-color: #fff;
      transition: transform 0.2s ease;
    }

    .hero-cta:hover span {
      transform: translateX(3px);
    }

    /* Gradient Mesh */
    .gradient-mesh {
      width: 100%;
      aspect-ratio: 4 / 3;
      border-radius: 24px;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      background:
        radial-gradient(ellipse at 20% 30%, #6366F1 0%, transparent 50%),
        radial-gradient(ellipse at 75% 25%, #F472B6 0%, transparent 45%),
        radial-gradient(ellipse at 60% 70%, #2DD4BF 0%, transparent 50%),
        radial-gradient(ellipse at 30% 80%, #FBBF24 0%, transparent 40%),
        radial-gradient(ellipse at 85% 75%, #8B5CF6 0%, transparent 45%);
      background-size: 200% 200%;
      animation: gradientShift 12s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
      box-shadow:
        0 24px 64px rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.2),
        0 8px 24px rgba(244, 114, 182, 0.15);
    }

    .gradient-mesh::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      border-radius: 24px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.25);
    }

    @keyframes gradientShift {
      0% { background-position: 0% 0%; }
      25% { background-position: 50% 25%; }
      50% { background-position: 100% 50%; }
      75% { background-position: 50% 75%; }
      100% { background-position: 0% 100%; }
    }

    /* Background decoration */
    .hero::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: -200px;
      right: -200px;
      width: 500px;
      height: 500px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.06) 0%, transparent 70%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    /* ===== SECTION: SERVICES ===== */
    .services {
      padding: 6rem 2rem;
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .section-label {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6366F1, #F472B6);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .section-title {
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      color: #1E1E2E;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }

    .services-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }

    .service-card {
      padding: 2rem;
      border-radius: 20px;
      background: #fff;
      border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
      transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .service-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-4px);
      box-shadow: 0 16px 48px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
    }

    .service-card::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      height: 4px;
      border-radius: 20px 20px 0 0;
    }

    .service-card:nth-child(1)::before {
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #6366F1, #8B5CF6);
    }

    .service-card:nth-child(2)::before {
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #F472B6, #FB923C);
    }

    .service-card:nth-child(3)::before {
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #2DD4BF, #6366F1);
    }

    .service-card-icon {
      width: 48px;
      height: 48px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    }

    .service-card:nth-child(1) .service-card-icon {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.12), rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.12));
    }

    .service-card:nth-child(2) .service-card-icon {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(244, 114, 182, 0.12), rgba(251, 146, 60, 0.12));
    }

    .service-card:nth-child(3) .service-card-icon {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(45, 212, 191, 0.12), rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.12));
    }

    .service-card-icon svg {
      width: 22px;
      height: 22px;
    }

    .service-card h3 {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
      color: #1E1E2E;
    }

    .service-card .card-scope {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #94A3B8;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .service-card p {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      color: #64748B;
      line-height: 1.65;
    }

    /* Stat banner */
    .stat-banner {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 1rem;
      padding: 2rem;
      border-radius: 20px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6366F1, #8B5CF6, #F472B6);
      color: #fff;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .stat-number {
      font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
      line-height: 1;
    }

    .stat-text {
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 400;
      opacity: 0.9;
      text-align: left;
      line-height: 1.4;
    }

    /* ===== SECTION: FARBBERATUNG ===== */
    .farbberatung {
      padding: 6rem 2rem;
      background: #F0FDF4;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .farbberatung::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      bottom: -100px;
      left: -100px;
      width: 400px;
      height: 400px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.05) 0%, transparent 70%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .farbberatung::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: -80px;
      right: -80px;
      width: 300px;
      height: 300px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(244, 114, 182, 0.05) 0%, transparent 70%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .farbberatung-inner {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
    }

    .farbberatung-content {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 4rem;
      align-items: start;
    }

    .farbberatung-text h2 {
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      color: #1E1E2E;
      margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    }

    .farbberatung-text h2 em {
      font-style: normal;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6366F1, #2DD4BF);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
    }

    .farbberatung-text p {
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      color: #64748B;
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .farbberatung-text .highlight {
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #6366F1;
    }

    .farbberatung-cta {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      padding: 0.8rem 1.8rem;
      border-radius: 50px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6366F1, #8B5CF6);
      color: #fff;
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      margin-top: 1rem;
      transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
    }

    .farbberatung-cta:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 12px 32px rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.3);
    }

    /* Color Palette */
    .palette-section {
      padding: 2rem;
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 20px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
    }

    .palette-title {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      color: #94A3B8;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .palette-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .swatch {
      text-align: center;
    }

    .swatch-color {
      width: 100%;
      aspect-ratio: 1;
      border-radius: 14px;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
      cursor: default;
    }

    .swatch-color:hover {
      transform: scale(1.06);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);
    }

    .swatch-name {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #1E1E2E;
      margin-bottom: 0.15rem;
    }

    .swatch-hex {
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      font-weight: 400;
      color: #94A3B8;
    }

    /* Owner */
    .owner-info {
      margin-top: 2rem;
      padding-top: 1.5rem;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .owner-avatar {
      width: 48px;
      height: 48px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6366F1, #F472B6);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      color: #fff;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .owner-name {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #1E1E2E;
    }

    .owner-role {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: #94A3B8;
    }

    /* ===== FOOTER ===== */
    .footer {
      padding: 3rem 2rem;
      text-align: center;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
    }

    .footer-brand {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6366F1, #F472B6);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .footer p {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: #94A3B8;
    }

    /* ===== RESPONSIVE ===== */
    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .hero-inner {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .hero-text {
        order: 2;
      }

      .gradient-mesh {
        order: 1;
        max-width: 480px;
        margin: 0 auto;
      }

      .hero-cta {
        margin: 0 auto;
      }

      .services-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        max-width: 480px;
        margin: 0 auto 3rem;
      }

      .farbberatung-content {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        gap: 2rem;
      }

      .palette-grid {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      }

      .stat-banner {
        flex-direction: column;
        max-width: 480px;
        margin: 0 auto;
      }

      .stat-text {
        text-align: center;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .navbar {
        padding: 0.75rem 1.25rem;
      }

      .navbar-links {
        display: none;
        position: absolute;
        top: 100%;
        left: 0;
        right: 0;
        flex-direction: column;
        background: rgba(250, 250, 250, 0.98);
        backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
        padding: 1.5rem;
        gap: 1.25rem;
        border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.12);
      }

      .navbar-links.open {
        display: flex;
      }

      .navbar-cta-wrap {
        display: none;
      }

      .menu-toggle {
        display: flex;
      }

      .hero {
        padding: 6rem 1.25rem 3rem;
        min-height: auto;
      }

      .services {
        padding: 4rem 1.25rem;
      }

      .farbberatung {
        padding: 4rem 1.25rem;
      }

      .palette-grid {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <!-- NAVBAR -->
  <nav class="navbar">
    <a href="/#hero" class="navbar-brand">Spektrum</a>
    <ul class="navbar-links" id="navLinks">
      <li><a href="/#leistungen">Leistungen</a></li>
      <li><a href="/#farbberatung">Farbberatung</a></li>
      <li><a href="/#kontakt">Kontakt</a></li>
    </ul>
    <div class="navbar-cta-wrap">
      <a href="/#kontakt" class="navbar-cta">Projekt anfragen</a>
    </div>
    <button class="menu-toggle" id="menuToggle" aria-label="Menu oeffnen">
      <span></span>
      <span></span>
      <span></span>
    </button>
  </nav>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="hero" id="hero">
    <div class="hero-inner">
      <div class="hero-text">
        <h1>Farbe <span>veraendert</span> alles.</h1>
        <p class="hero-subtitle">
          <strong>Malerbetrieb & Farbgestaltung</strong> &middot; Trier &middot; Seit 2011
        </p>
        <a href="/#kontakt" class="hero-cta">
          Projekt anfragen <span>&rarr;</span>
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="gradient-mesh" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SERVICES -->
  <section class="services" id="leistungen">
    <p class="section-label">Leistungen</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">Was ich mache</h2>

    <div class="services-grid">
      <!-- Card 1 -->
      <div class="service-card">
        <div class="service-card-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#6366F1" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2" />
            <line x1="3" y1="9" x2="21" y2="9" />
            <line x1="9" y1="3" x2="9" y2="21" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Fassadengestaltung</h3>
        <p class="card-scope">Aussen</p>
        <p>Farbkonzepte, die zur Architektur passen und dem Gebaeude Charakter geben. Von der Planung bis zum letzten Anstrich.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 2 -->
      <div class="service-card">
        <div class="service-card-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#F472B6" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M3 9l9-7 9 7v11a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2z" />
            <polyline points="9 22 9 12 15 12 15 22" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Innenraumkonzepte</h3>
        <p class="card-scope">Wohn & Gewerbe</p>
        <p>Raeume, die wirken. Farblich abgestimmte Konzepte fuer Wohnungen, Bueros, Praxen und Laeden in der Region.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 3 -->
      <div class="service-card">
        <div class="service-card-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#2DD4BF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5z" />
            <path d="M2 17l10 5 10-5" />
            <path d="M2 12l10 5 10-5" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Kreative Techniken</h3>
        <p class="card-scope">Spachteltechnik, Marmorierung</p>
        <p>Oberfaechen mit Tiefe und Struktur. Individuelle Veredelung fuer Waende, die mehr koennen als nur Farbe tragen.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="stat-banner">
      <span class="stat-number">380+</span>
      <span class="stat-text">gestrichene Raeume<br />seit 2011</span>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FARBBERATUNG -->
  <section class="farbberatung" id="farbberatung">
    <div class="farbberatung-inner">
      <div class="farbberatung-content">
        <div class="farbberatung-text">
          <p class="section-label">Farbberatung</p>
          <h2>Jeder Raum hat <em>seine Farbe</em>. Ich finde sie.</h2>
          <p>
            Farbe ist mehr als Geschmack. Sie beeinflusst Stimmung, Raumwirkung und Wohlbefinden. In meiner kostenlosen Erstberatung analysiere ich den Raum, das Licht und den Zweck &mdash; und entwickle daraus ein Farbkonzept, das passt.
          </p>
          <p>
            <span class="highlight">Kostenlose Erstberatung</span> &mdash; vor Ort in Trier und Umgebung.
          </p>
          <a href="/#kontakt" class="farbberatung-cta">
            Beratung anfragen &rarr;
          </a>

          <div class="owner-info">
            <div class="owner-avatar">SK</div>
            <div>
              <div class="owner-name">Stefan Kraemer</div>
              <div class="owner-role">Malermeister &middot; Spektrum Trier</div>
